Because patches only modify local files in your League directory, they're *extremely unlikely* to affect your connection to the servers. Changes in latency (ping) are typically caused by ISP routing to the server or local network configurations. Since there are a number of steps that can be taken to troubleshoot this issue, I recommend taking a look at our [connection troubleshooting guide.
](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues)

Let me know if this causes any change for your connection.
